<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>does not <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citing_sources" title="Wikipedia:Citing sources">cite</a> any <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Verifiability" title="Wikipedia:Verifiability">references or sources</a></b>. Please help <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Tagalog_grammar&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Tagalog_grammar&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this article</a> by adding citations to <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Reliable_sources" title="Wikipedia:Reliable sources">reliable sources</a> (ideally, using <i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Footnotes" title="Wikipedia:Footnotes">inline citations</a></i>). Unsourced material may be <a href="/wiki/Template:Fact" title="Template:Fact">challenged</a> and <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:BURDEN" title="Wikipedia:BURDEN" class="mw-redirect">removed</a>. <small><i>(May 2008)</i></small></td>
