<p>This article describes the grammar of <a href="/wiki/Tagalog_language" title="Tagalog language">Tagalog</a> (the language of the Tagalog region of the Philippines) and <a href="/wiki/Filipino_language" title="Filipino language">Filipino</a> (the national language of the Philippines).</p>
